{"name":"Canalisation d'énergie divine [Serment d'aliénation] Ennemi mortel","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-yellow-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.JnapZCJGLbUJ2qeu"}},"_id":"1tAp58zRiINJZ5lO","system":{"description":{"value":"<h4 id=\"canalisation-d-energie-divine-4\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#2e1f49;font-family:Friz, sans-serif;font-size:13px\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Canalisation d'énergie divine</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Quand vous prêtez votre serment au niveau 3, vous accédez aux deux options suivantes de canalisation d'énergie divine.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"><span style=\"color:#2e1f49;font-family:Friz, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><strong>Ennemi mortel : </strong>En utilisant votre action bonus et en dépensant votre canalisation d'énergie divine, vous pouvez désigner une cible que vous voyez située au plus à 9 mètres et en faire l'ennemi mortel de votre Sire. Vous avez désormais l'<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a> à toutes vos attaques contre cette créature. Ce pouvoir prend fin au bout d'une minute, si vous tombez à 0 point de vie ou <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#inconscient\">inconscient</a>.</span></span></p>\n<h4 id=\"canalisation-d-energie-divine-2\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#2e1f49;font-family:Friz, sans-serif;font-size:13px\"></h4>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685156,"modifiedTime":1663923686042,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"1tKqUMeYwLyEP2mi","name":"Serment d'Obédience [Paladin]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lnbbFVqnvyBSMFCa"}},"img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-shield-white-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience</strong></h3>\n<p>Quand vous atteignez le niveau 3, vous pr&ecirc;tez un serment qui vous engage &agrave; tout jamais. Jusqu'&agrave; ce moment-l&agrave;, vous &eacute;tiez encore &agrave; un stade pr&eacute;paratoire, engag&eacute; dans la voie, mais sans vous y &ecirc;tre enti&egrave;rement d&eacute;vou&eacute;.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Votre choix vous permet d'avoir acc&egrave;s &agrave; des aptitudes particuli&egrave;res aux niveaux 3, 7, 15 et 20. Parmi ces aptitudes se trouvent les sorts de serment et la canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.KFmbT4ZTufmoDEZb]{Pr&eacute;ceptes d'ob&eacute;dience [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience]}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Niveau 3 : </strong>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.KWz8TVQ6QulQrKQS]{Sorts de serment [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience]}</p>\n<p><strong>Niveau 3 : </strong>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.IgBj0bMjSEwiWRek]{Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience] Porte-&eacute;tendard} @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.hQxW6q6iI30bJZ1l]{Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience] Tacticien}</p>\n<p><strong>Niveau 7 :</strong> @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.6QUbP3zHUfyNHh4G]{Cri de ralliement [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience]}</p>\n<p><strong>Niveau 15 :</strong> @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.WX2Fmh3H0y0Ianq8]{Charge h&eacute;ro&iuml;que [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience]}</p>\n<p><strong>Niveau 20 : </strong>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.CnIYOXfad2SYzbXT]{H&eacute;ros de Guerre [Serment d'Ob&eacute;dience]}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685157,"modifiedTime":1663923686044,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
