{"_id":"27dJNNk7X889wNXD","name":"Endurci [Arpenteur]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/control/control-influence-rally-purple.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"endurci\"><strong>Endurci</strong></h3>\n<p>D&egrave;s le niveau 2, vous &ecirc;tes habitu&eacute; &agrave; la vie en plein air et &agrave; affronter les dangers du monde. Vous pouvez choisir une comp&eacute;tence que vous ma&icirc;trisez d&eacute;sormais parmi Athl&eacute;tisme, Discr&eacute;tion, Nature, Perception ou Survie. De plus, vous choisissez comme arme de pr&eacute;dilection n'importe quelle arme de corps-&agrave;-corps qui n'a pas les propri&eacute;t&eacute;s lourde ou &agrave; deux mains. Vous obtenez la ma&icirc;trise de cette arme, et lorsque vous tenez votre arme de pr&eacute;dilection, vous b&eacute;n&eacute;ficiez en permanence du sort d'@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.lebzBItGh48POCUX]{Armure du mage}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVe