{"_id":"6S2sY22CUUNzPSMF","name":"Ancêtre Fiélon [Lignée infernale]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-small-red.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"ancetre-fielon\"><strong>Anc&ecirc;tre fi&eacute;lon</strong></h3>\n<p>Vous pouvez parler, lire et &eacute;crire en infernal ou en abyssal selon que votre lign&eacute;e descende des d&eacute;mons ou des diables.</p>\n<p>De plus, &agrave; chaque fois que vous faites un test de Charisme alors que vous interagissez avec des fi&eacute;lons, votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise est doubl&eacute; s'il s'applique.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Ensorceleur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685192,"modifiedTime":1663923686178,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"6YAFzkkPtf5CwS0a","name":"Sorts de prédilection [Magicien]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":53},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"sorts-de-predilection\"><strong>Sorts de pr&eacute;dilection</strong></h3>\n<p>Quand vous atteignez le niveau 20, vous ma&icirc;trisez deux puissants sorts que vous pouvez lancer tr&egrave;s facilement. Choisissez deux sorts de niveau 3 dans votre grimoire, qui deviendront vos sorts de pr&eacute;dilection. Ces sorts sont toujours consid&eacute;r&eacute;s comme pr&eacute;par&eacute;s mais ne sont pas comptabilis&eacute;s dans votre nombre de sorts pr&eacute;par&eacute;s. Vous pouvez lancer chacun d'eux une fois au niveau 3 sans utiliser d'emplacement de sort. Une fois que vous avez lanc&eacute; un de ces sorts ou les deux, vous ne pouvez pas les relancer gratuitement tant que vous n'avez pas termin&eacute; un repos court ou un repos long.</p>\n<p>Si vous voulez lancer un de ces sorts &agrave; un niveau sup&eacute;rieur, vous &ecirc;tes soumis &agrave; la r&egrave;gle normale et devez utiliser un emplacement de sort.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":"","type":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versa