{"_id":"92cNRurZalXAZFd4","name":"Attaques multiples - Attaque tourbillonnante [Chasseur]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lJUeVvdUxRYpGl7J"}},"img":"icons/skills/ranged/target-bullseye-arrow-white.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Attaques Multiples</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Au niveau 11, vous pouvez choisir l'une des deux aptitudes suivantes : Salve ou Attaque tourbillonnante.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Attaque tourbillonnante</strong>. Vous pouvez utiliser votre action pour faire une attaque de corps-&agrave;-corps contre autant de cr&eacute;atures que vous le souhaitez dans la mesure o&ugrave; elles se trouvent dans un rayon de 1,50 m&egrave;tre autour de vous, en faisant un&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#jets-d-attaque\">jet d'attaque</a>&nbsp;s&eacute;par&eacute; pour chaque cr&eacute;ature.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","create