{"_id":"BOpwKUCEIaBhyZpv","name":"Déplacement souterrain [Cercle des profondeurs]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"icons/magic/air/wind-vortex-swirl-purple.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"deplacement-souterrain\"><strong>D&eacute;placement souterrain</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 14, vous pouvez vous d&eacute;placer &agrave; travers la pierre ou la terre d'un sol ou d'une paroi, s'ils sont naturels, &agrave; la moiti&eacute; de votre vitesse normale, que ce soit sous votre forme normale ou sous forme sauvage. Vous devez terminer votre d&eacute;placement &agrave; l'air libre. Si ce n'est pas le cas, vous subissez 2d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts par tour, seulement la moiti&eacute; si vous r&eacute;ussissez un jet de sauvegarde de Constitution DD 15.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685228,"modifiedTime":1663923686307,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
