{"_id":"Do3ZVyD4fzrQ0Yvv","name":"Puissance élémentaire Eau Déluge [Élémentaliste]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PXkkeQOdHJ1cpTcK"}},"img":"icons/magic/water/pseudopod-swirl-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h4 id=\"puissance-elementaire\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Puissance &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&Eacute;galement &agrave; partir du niveau 2, vous pouvez invoquer l'&eacute;nergie de votre &eacute;l&eacute;ment de pr&eacute;dilection pour cr&eacute;er un effet magique. Choisissez une seule aptitude parmi les deux propos&eacute;s pour chaque &eacute;l&eacute;ment. Vous devez terminer un repos court ou long avant de pouvoir &agrave; nouveau utiliser votre pouvoir &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Eau</strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Vous gagnez le pouvoir surnaturel d&eacute;luge ou d&eacute;charge glaciale.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">D&eacute;luge</strong>. En utilisant une action, vous invoquez une masse d'eau du plan &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire qui s'abat autour de vous. Chaque cr&eacute;ature situ&eacute;e &agrave; 1,50 m&egrave;tre ou moins de vous doit effectuer un&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute;. En cas d'&eacute;chec, elle subit 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts contondant et est&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#repousse\">repouss&eacute;e</a>&nbsp;de 1,50 m&egrave;tre de vous.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts augmentent de 1d6 lorsque vous atteignez le niveau 5 (2d6), le niveau 11 (3d6) et le niveau 17 (4d6).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"JdS Echec : 1d6 dégâts contondant et est repoussée de 1,50 mètre de vous - JdS réussi : Pas d'effet","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685244,"modifiedTime":1663923686375,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"DtIApEucRughBwNE","name":"Magie académique [Académicien]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-swirling-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"magie-academique\"><strong>Magie acad&eacute;mique</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 2, puis &agrave; chaque fois que vous gagnez un niveau, vous inscrivez dans votre grimoire et vous apprenez un sort suppl&eacute;mentaire qui doit &ecirc;tre issu de votre &eacute;cole. Lorsque vous obtenez l'aptitude ma&icirc;trise des sorts (au niveau 18), vous devez choisir des sorts de votre &eacute;cole. Lorsque vous obtenez l'aptitude sorts de pr&eacute;dilection (au niveau 20), vous devez choisir au moins un sort de votre &eacute;cole.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685245,"modifiedTime":1663923686377,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"E7ltJtz4EFjaZRXD","name":"Réaction rapide [Cercle de la Vie]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.r209FURENC8upKud"}},"img":"icons/magic/air/wind-stream-blue-gray.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Gazette R'n P #3</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 10, vous &ecirc;tes toujours prompt &agrave; aider vos alli&eacute;s. Quand l&rsquo;un de vos alli&eacute;s subit des dommages, vous pouvez utiliser votre r&eacute;action afin de lancer @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.k2lRJF0cIp0fJn5I]{Soin des blessures} ou @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.q4YQyD1xulTcHEgm]{Mot de gu&eacute;rison}.</p>\n<p>Si votre alli&eacute; devait tomber &agrave; 0 PV, il serait alors consid&eacute;r&eacute; comme ayant un nombre de PV &eacute;gal au r&eacute;sultat de votre sort de soins et ne tombe pas inconscient. Vous devez cependant utiliser un emplacement de sort. Vous pouvez, &agrave; la place, utiliser votre capacit&eacute; @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.kOCDaMSafDcQvCRs]{Gu&eacute;risseur &eacute;m&eacute;rite [Cercle de la Vie]} et d&eacute;penser une m&eacute;tamorphose afin de lancer @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.k2lRJF0cIp0fJn5I]{Soin des blessures}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #3","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":