{"_id":"E8WAO0WmdkgdootW","name":"Riposte inattendue [Kal'Thori]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UwYVYYTkQJdvD0tk"}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/shield-damaged-broken-gold.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Riposte inattendue</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 18, lorsqu&rsquo;une attaque devrait vous toucher, vous pouvez utiliser votre r&eacute;action afin d&rsquo;obtenir la r&eacute;sistance contre les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de l&rsquo;attaque.</p>\n<p>De plus, s&rsquo;il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;une attaque de corps &agrave; corps, vous parvenez &agrave; d&eacute;vier la puissance du coup pour la retourner contre votre adversaire en d&eacute;portant son coup afin qu&rsquo;il heurte le d&eacute;cor. Il subit la moiti&eacute; des points de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts que vous avez subis.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #2","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685246,"modifiedTime":1663923686382,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
