{"_id":"IL0TGibuXpuXFgLm","name":"Main dans la main [Collège des Saltimbanques]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-smoke-teal.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"main-dans-la-main\"><strong>Main dans la main</strong></h3>\n<p>D'o&ugrave; vous venez, la solidarit&eacute; n'est pas un vain mot, et vous avez appris chez les saltimbanques &agrave; travailler main dans la main avec vos &eacute;quipiers. &Agrave; partir du niveau 3 &eacute;galement, lorsque vous faites un test de groupe (voir la section&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#travailler-ensemble\">Travailler ensemble</a>&nbsp;du chapitre&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/\">Utiliser les caract&eacute;ristiques</a>), en cas de succ&egrave;s de votre test, vous comptabilisez deux succ&egrave;s.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Barde","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685281,"modifiedTime":1663923686533,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Esprit de Vie [Cercle de la Vie]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.etpQ8k1Je9YtSMKX"}},"img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-green.webp","effects":[],"_id":"IMAD3bZa3nabKZnH","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Esprit de Vie</p>\n<p>Au niveau 18, en plus de vos aptitudes de druide, vous pouvez canaliser la puissance vitale de la nature &agrave; travers votre corps.</p>\n<p>En utilisant votre action, vous commencez &agrave; vous nourrir de l&rsquo;&eacute;nergie tellurique autour de vous.</p>\n<p>Au d&eacute;but de chacun de vos tours, et durant une minute, vous regagnez un nombre de points de vie &eacute;gal &agrave; la moiti&eacute; de votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise.</p>\n<p>Si vous tombez inconscient, l&rsquo;effet continue. Si vous &eacute;tiez &agrave; 0 PV, vous &ecirc;tes automatiquement stabilis&eacute; au d&eacute;but de votre tour suivant et vous redevenez conscient en plus de regagner des points de vie.</p>\n<p>Vous devez effectuer un repos long avant de pouvoir utiliser de nouveau cette capacit&eacute;.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #3","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["@prof / 2","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685281,"modifiedTime":1663923686535,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
