{"_id":"JrWtl7bcIAgMdlbt","name":"Tradition arcanique [Magicien]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/water/orb-ice-glow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":49},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.FWOQNpnsvihajpYm"},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Quand vous atteignez le niveau 2, vous choisissez une <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/classes/magicien/#traditions-arcaniques\">tradition arcanique</a> qui définit votre manière de pratiquer la magie. Les traditions disponibles sont : </p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.SbrTKYTvqwStUQFy]{[Magicien] Académicien}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.EXCzy8yV2gQYOOW0]{[Magicien] Arpenteur}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.Wl01RHUeHfkI2vHq]{[Magicien] École d'évocation}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.5DGr66hWelbROKos]{[Magicien] Élémentaliste}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.a4c1iDkc06yTrDfe]{[Magicien] Éminence grise}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.MUKtiEA81Ed2yEzZ]{[Magicien] Mage de guerre}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.lt5iln4PHifno3OV]{[Magicien] Maître d'étude}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":"","type":""},"consume":{"typ