{"name":"Magie des morts","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/ankh-gold-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ySmSU6sToXZC8MqU"}},"_id":"O1G2m10MXldYs8Ah","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Au niveau 2, vous apprenez les tours de magie@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.U9cAaSWID7Xp0a8w]{Contact glacial} et @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.cp90m51PmZofavuP]{Épargner les mourants}.</p>\n<p>De plus, vous pouvez dépenser une utilisation de votre forme sauvage pour lancer un sort de cercle (cf. ci-après) sans dépenser d'emplacement de sort.</p>\n<p>Enfin, vous bénéficiez d'un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a> à tous les tests de Charisme que vous effectuez pour interagir avec des créatures de la catégorie des morts-vivants.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>À partir du niveau 20, vous pouvez utiliser une de vos utilisations de forme sauvage afin de lancer un sort de cercle trois fois, au maximum, entre deux repos courts ou longs.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685376,"modifiedTime":1663923686726,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Ennemi des ténèbres","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-contained-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">À partir du niveau 10, votre foi et votre entraînement font de vous un ennemi redoutable des créatures des ténèbres. Une fois par tour, vous pouvez obtenir un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage </a>sur un jet d'attaque ou un test de caractéristique effectué contre un fiélon, un mort-vivant ou une créature de l'ombre.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Warlock Grimoire - Kobold Press","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Lancier du crépuscule","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"MB7dftOsMOjK5aEw":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1a2lRcIjMn213VOr"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1678361234172,"modifiedTime":1678361380822,"lastModifiedBy":"MB7dftOsMOjK5aEw"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"O3bMGs9sybXu3T5Z"}
{"name":"Action coordonnée","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-handshake-gray.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Tsn3yMAeTwhD5o6u"}},"_id":"O9AjCJ7qBRYlJ6vD","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Au niveau 18, lorsque vous utilisez votre sursaut d'activité, désignez un allié dans un rayon de 18 m. Ce dernier doit être capable de vous entendre et de vous comprendre. Utilisez votre réaction et dépensez deux dés de commandement. Votre allié bénéficie aussi des effets de la capacité @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.5C1yFuTrJyvHLbBp]{Sursaut d'activité [Guerrier]}. Cependant, il lui est impossible de lancer un sort grâce aux effets du sursaut d'activité</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette Role'n Play #7","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier / Officier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685377,"modifiedTime":1663923686728,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"OCb9Z6mN42ntD2Ze","name":"Frappe des arcanes [Sorcelame]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-teal-purple.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"frappe-des-arcanes\"><strong>Frappe des arcanes</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 7, vous pouvez d&eacute;penser 1 point de sorcellerie et une action bonus pour charger votre arme de l'&eacute;nergie de la magie. Vous ajoutez 1d4 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force &agrave; tous vos jets de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts avec cette arme pendant ce round. Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s avec l'arme sont consid&eacute;r&eacute;s comme des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts magiques lorsque vous &ecirc;tes confront&eacute; &agrave; des r&eacute;sistances ou des immunit&eacute;s aux attaques et aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts non magiques.</p>\n<p>Si vous utilisez, dans le m&ecirc;me round, la capacit&eacute; @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.5C1yFuTrJyvHLbBp]{Sursaut d'activit&eacute; [Guerrier]}, vous devez d&eacute;penser 1 point de sorcellerie suppl&eacute;mentaire afin de b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier de cette capacit&eacute;.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685377,"modified