{"_id":"PYNBwYPDtlwbPB8G","name":"Terrain de prédilection [Traqueur]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/environment/wilderness/cave-entrance-mountain-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"terrain-de-predilection\"><strong>Terrain de pr&eacute;dilection</strong></h3>\n<p>D&egrave;s le niveau 3, vous faites l'acquisition d'un second terrain de pr&eacute;dilection. De plus vous ajoutez les profondeurs (milieu naturel souterrain) &agrave; la liste des terrains de pr&eacute;dilection qui vous sont accessibles.</p>\n<h4 id=\"maitre-du-terrain\"></h4>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685383,"modifiedTime":1663923686754,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"PYsBWYQE2hG8TSMq","name":"Canalisation d'énergie divine [Serment de Piété] Inquisiteur","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uZc1vdhqfeYRmE7C"}},"img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-yellow-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h4 id=\"canalisation-d-energie-divine-5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Quand vous pr&ecirc;tez votre serment au niveau 3, vous acc&eacute;dez aux deux options suivantes de canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Inquisiteur</strong>. Au prix d'une action, vous invoquez la puissance de votre dieu et brandissez votre symbole sacr&eacute; en utilisant votre canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine. Choisissez une cr&eacute;ature dans un rayon de 9 m&egrave;tres autour de vous. Cette cr&eacute;ature est&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#repousse\">repouss&eacute;e</a>&nbsp;pendant 1 minute si elle rate un&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Sagesse. Si son alignement comprend au moins une composante oppos&eacute;e &agrave; l'alignement de votre dieu tut&eacute;laire (exemple : Chaotique pour un dieu Loyal, Bon pour un dieu Mauvais, etc.), la cr&eacute;ature subit un&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">d&eacute;savantage</a>&nbsp;sur ce&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>. Les cr&eacute;atures non align&eacute;es sont immunis&eacute;es &agrave; cette capacit&eacute;.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":9,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"JdS Echec : créature repoussée pendant 1 minute - Désavantage au JdS si une composante de l'alignement est opposée","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685384,"modifiedTime":1663923686756,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"PbpbAUqxp6llFD7e","name":"Inspirer la bravoure [Collège des Hérauts]","type":"feat","img":"icons/sundries/flags/banner-symbol-axe-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"betterRolls5e":{"critRange":{"value":null},"critDamage":{"value":""},"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"inspirer-la-bravoure\"><strong>Inspirer la bravoure</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 14, sur un champ de bataille, votre simple pr&eacute;sence assure les protagonistes que leurs exploits ne seront pas oubli&eacute;s, les poussant &agrave; toujours plus de bravoure ! Durant un combat, vous pouvez d&eacute;penser une@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.VXRpFFtML2YSlPTA]{Inspirations Bardique [Barde]} et utiliser une action bonus pour permettre &agrave; tous vos alli&eacute;s &agrave; moins de 18 m&egrave;tres de lancer un d&eacute; d'inspiration bardique et d'ajouter le r&eacute;sultat &agrave; l'un de leurs jets d'attaque avant votre prochain tour. Ils peuvent aussi ajouter ce r&eacute;sultat &agrave; tous les jets de sauvegarde contre l'effet <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#terrorise\">terroris&eacute;</a> pour la m&ecirc;me dur&eacute;e.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":18,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per"