{"_id":"UFEljDB6h0T1P9el","name":"Déplacement élémentaire Terre [Élémentaliste]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"icons/magic/earth/volcano-explosion-lava-yellow.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"deplacement-elementaire\"><strong>D&eacute;placement &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 10 vous gagnez l'aptitude suivante li&eacute;e &agrave; votre &eacute;l&eacute;ment de pr&eacute;dilection.</p>\n<p><strong>Terre :</strong>&nbsp;Tel un animal fouisseur, vous pouvez vous d&eacute;placer dans la terre d'un sol naturel &agrave; la moiti&eacute; de votre vitesse de d&eacute;placement. De plus, vous gagnez le sens <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/comprendre-le-profil-technique-des-monstres/#perception-des-vibrations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">perception des vibrations</a>&nbsp;(9 m&egrave;tres) lorsque vous vous d&eacute;placez de cette fa&ccedil;on. Vous devez terminer votre d&eacute;placement &agrave; l'air libre ou subir 4d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts contondants.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685409,"modifiedTime":1663923686865,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"UJpcy1WsNylCx6w7","name":"Lire sur les lèvres [Espion]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/commodities/currency/coin-engraved-sun-smile-copper.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h4 id=\"lire-sur-les-levres\"><strong>Lire sur les lèvres&nbsp;</strong></h4>\n<p>À partir du niveau 9, vous devenez capable de lire sur les lèvres ce que dit quelqu'un que vous n'entendez pas mais dont vous pouvez voir le visage. Vous devez réussir un test de Sagesse (Perception) dont la difficulté est égale à la moitié de la distance en mètres entre vous et votre cible (avec un minimum de 10 si la cible est à moins de 20 mètres). Vous subissez un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">désavantage</a> si votre cible est dans une zone de lumière faible.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Roublard","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685409,"modifiedTime":1663923686868,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Artillerie lourde [Mage de guerre]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-embers-orange.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lpIv6GJty1ijCqiM"}},"_id":"UJrmaI8wtDC0xjVp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 6, lorsque vous lancez un sort avec un effet de zone, vous pouvez le lancer avec un emplacement de sort d'un niveau au-dessus pour doubler la surface du sort.</p>\n<p>Les zones doivent être au contact l'une de l'autre (par exemple une @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.bvRksmepD9SBn5fv]{Boule de feu} affecte deux zones adjacente de 12 mètres).</p>\n<p>Vous devez prendre un repos court avant de pouvoir à nouveau utiliser cette aptitude sans vous épuiser. Dans le cas contraire, vous subissez un niveau d'épuisement.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685409,"modifiedTime":1663923686871,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
