{"_id":"UXay6APy4K2yZjlJ","name":"À demi-mort [Seigneur Immortel]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":true,"effects":[{"modSpecKey":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"necrotic","mode":"+","targetSpecific":false,"id":1,"itemId":"UXay6APy4K2yZjlJ","active":false,"_targets":[],"label":"Traits Résistance"},{"modSpecKey":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"cold","mode":"+","targetSpecific":false,"id":2,"itemId":"UXay6APy4K2yZjlJ","active":false,"_targets":[],"label":"Traits Résistance"},{"modSpecKey":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"poison","mode":"+","targetSpecific":false,"id":3,"itemId":"UXay6APy4K2yZjlJ","active":false,"_targets":[]}]}},"img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"a-demi-mort\"><strong>&Agrave; demi-mort</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 14, les terribles secrets que vous ma&icirc;trisez transforment irr&eacute;m&eacute;diablement votre corps, et vous franchissez un premier pas vers la non-vie et l'&eacute;ternit&eacute;. D&eacute;sormais, vous obtenez la r&eacute;sistance aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts n&eacute;crotiques, de froid et de poison. Vous n'avez plus besoin de respirer ni de manger ou de boire et votre esp&eacute;rance de vie est doubl&eacute;e. Votre corps devient froid au toucher. Enfin, la difficult&eacute; du&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a> de votre pacte avec la Mort est abaiss&eacute;e de 5 points.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"vers