{"_id":"VjfjCI4WdMlD1eBN","name":"Résistance des arcanes [Sorcelame]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"resistance-des-arcanes\"><strong>R&eacute;sistance des arcanes</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 10, vous pouvez d&eacute;penser votre r&eacute;action et 1 point de sorcellerie pour obtenir un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;&agrave; un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de votre choix contre un sort ou un effet magique.</p>\n<p>&Agrave; ce niveau, en plus du sort que vous apprenez normalement, vous apprenez un troisi&egrave;me tour de magie de la liste de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/grimoire/?classes=Ensorceleur%2FSorcelame\">sorts de sorcelame</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685424,"modifiedTime":1663923686935,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Régénération [Voie des fleurs]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-beam-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.m5j4UBVyOTNZpKWZ"}},"_id":"W7iuXqe9KNmCdech","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 17, vous pouvez régénérer votre énergie vitale en laissant l'énergie du sol remonter à travers vos pieds et circuler en vous, à la façon dont un arbre fait repousser les branches taillées lorsque le printemps arrive.</p>\n<p>En dépensant 6 points de Ki, vous pouvez lancer le sort @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.sAikSaD9j0EhrsS1]{Régénération} sur vous-même tant que vous avez les pieds en contact avec la terre.</p>\n<p>Le sort cesse de faire effet si vous vous déplacez.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez utiliser cette aptitude une fois entre deux repos longs.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":6},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Moine","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685425,"modifiedTime":1663923686938,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
