{"_id":"Z5SW9uqtlmIO5ooQ","name":"Tour silencieux [Éminence grise]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-small-teal.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"tour-silencieux\"><strong>Tour silencieux</strong></h3>\n<p>Vous pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez &eacute;viter l'emploi de la violence pour r&eacute;gler vos affaires. Toutefois, lorsque cela devient n&eacute;cessaire, vous savez le faire efficacement et silencieusement, de fa&ccedil;on &agrave; ne pas laisser de t&eacute;moin g&ecirc;nant. &Eacute;galement &agrave; partir du niveau 6, vous pouvez lancer vos tours de magie sans composante vocale. Lorsque vous utilisez un tour de magie qui n&eacute;cessite un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#jets-d-attaque\">jet d'attaque</a>, vous infligez 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts suppl&eacute;mentaires si vous avez un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;sur ce&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#jets-d-attaque\">jet d'attaque</a>. Au niveau 10, ce bonus passe &agrave; 2d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts et au niveau 14 &agrave; 3d6. Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts sont du m&ecirc;me type que ceux du sort.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":