{"_id":"auqHEfFaOZTfWGt0","name":"Déplacement sans armure [Moine]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/social/intimidation-impressing.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"deplacement-sans-armure\"><strong>Déplacement sans armure</strong></h3>\n<p>À partir du niveau 2, votre vitesse augmente de 3 mètres tant que vous ne portez pas d'armure ni de bouclier. Ce bonus s'accroît en même temps que vos niveaux, comme indiqué dans le tableau du @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-Classes-spécialisations.doKdvMxZr8YJSEr4]{Moine}.</p>\n<p>Au niveau 9, vous gagnez la capacité de vous déplacer sans chuter sur des surfaces verticales ou sur des liquides pendant votre tour, tant que vous finissez votre mouvement sur une surface plane et solide.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Moine","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685457,"modifiedTime":1663923687072,"lastModifiedBy":"