{"name":"Attaque par surprise [Kalanthe]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-dagger-skull-white.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.IVA4BIhvCg7evMIr"}},"_id":"cj1EfNeB2P35USt7","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Également au niveau 3, lorsque vous attaquez un adversaire <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#surpris\">surpris</a>, vous obtenez un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a> à votre attaque. En cas de réussite, vous infligez +2d6 dégâts qui peuvent se cumuler aux dés acquis par une attaque sournoise.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Roublard","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685471,"modifiedTime":1663923687130,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"ckMdRz2DR3BIxEBn","name":"Pièges [Traqueur]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/environment/traps/trap-jaw-steel.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"pieges\"><strong>Pi&egrave;ges&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n<p>&Eacute;galement au niveau 3, lorsque vous &ecirc;tes sur votre terrain de pr&eacute;dilection, vous &ecirc;tes capable de pi&eacute;ger une zone de 3 m&egrave;tres de c&ocirc;t&eacute; en seulement 5 minutes. Toute cr&eacute;ature qui s'appr&ecirc;te &agrave; entrer dans la zone pi&eacute;g&eacute;e doit faire un test de Sagesse (Perception) pour d&eacute;tecter le pi&egrave;ge (difficult&eacute; &eacute;quivalente &agrave; un sort). Vous pouvez choisir l'effet du pi&egrave;ge parmi deux variantes :</p>\n<p><strong>Pi&egrave;ge l&eacute;tal</strong>&nbsp;(projectile, fosse, chausse-trappe, etc.). Inflige 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts par point de bonus de ma&icirc;trise. Si la victime r&eacute;ussit un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute;, elle ne subit que la moiti&eacute; des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts.</p>\n<p><strong>Pi&egrave;ge immobilisant</strong>&nbsp;(filet, collet, liane, etc.). La victime est&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#entrave\">entrav&eacute;e</a>&nbsp;pendant 2d6 rounds. &Agrave; son tour, elle peut utiliser son action pour se d&eacute;livrer en r&eacute;ussissant une sauvegarde de Force ou de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute; au choix.</p>\n<p>Le DD est de 8 + votre modificateur de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute; + votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise. Vous pouvez poser un pi&egrave;ge en seulement 1d6 rounds, mais la victime obtient un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;&agrave; son test de comp&eacute;tence pour le d&eacute;tecter. Si vous passez 1 heure &agrave; poser un pi&egrave;ge, la victime subit un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">d&eacute;savantage</a>&nbsp;&agrave; son test pour le d&eacute;tecter et pour en r&eacute;duire l'effet.</p>\n<p>Un pi&egrave;ge qui a affect&eacute; une cr&eacute;ature n'est plus actif. Il peut &ecirc;tre r&eacute;amorc&eacute; en seulement 1d6 rounds.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":5,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":3,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"square"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["(@prof)d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685471,"modifiedTime":1663923687132,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"cwFMPuHX2haHvan2","name":"Affinité élémentaire [Lignée draconique]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"betterRolls5e":{"critRange":{"value":null},"critDamage":{"value":""},"quickDesc":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickProperties":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickOther":{"value":true,"altValue":true},"quickFlavor":{"value":true,"altValue":true}}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"affinite-elementaire\"><strong>Affinit&eacute; &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 6, quand vous lancez un sort qui inflige des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts du type associ&eacute; &agrave; votre h&eacute;ritage draconique, vous pouvez ajouter votre modificateur de Charisme &agrave; ces d&eacute;g&acirc;ts. Vous pouvez dans le m&ecirc;me temps d&eacute;penser 1 point de sorcellerie pour devenir r&eacute;sistant &agrave; ce type de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts pendant 1 heure.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Ensorceleur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685472,"modifiedTime":1663923687134,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
