{"name":"La tête en bas","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-chains-ropes-net-purple-blue.webp","effects":[],"_id":"d7MMbJGmPfNVZM9o","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Au niveau 7 &eacute;galement, vous apprenez le sort @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.l4VPktMLaUOSFAEI]{Pattes d'araign&eacute;e} et vous pouvez le lancer, uniquement sur vous-m&ecirc;me, sans d&eacute;penser d'emplacement de sorts une fois entre deux repos courts ou longs.</p>\n<p>Si vous &ecirc;tes sur votre <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/classes/rodeur/#terrain-de-predilection\">terrain de pr&eacute;dilection</a>, la dur&eacute;e du sort est doubl&eacute;e</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette Role'n Play #5","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rodeur Passeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685473,"modifiedTime":1663923687138,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"d9HPKiJE7ydpsWIH","name":"Canalisation d’énergie divine [Clerc] Renvoi des Morts-vivants","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-smoke-yellow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"entityorder":{"order":129},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"canalisation-d-energie-divine-renvoi-des-morts-vivants\"><strong>Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine : Renvoi des morts-vivants</strong></h3>\n<p>Vous pouvez utiliser une action pour brandir votre symbole sacr&eacute; et prononcer une pri&egrave;re contre les morts-vivants. Dans un rayon de 9 m&egrave;tres, chaque mort-vivant qui peut vous voir ou vous entendre doit faire un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a> de Sagesse. Si une cr&eacute;ature &eacute;choue &agrave; son jet de sauvegarde, elle est&nbsp;repouss&eacute;e&nbsp;pendant 1 minute ou jusqu'&agrave; ce qu'elle subisse des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":9,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"JdS Echec : Repoussée pendant 1 minutes ou