{"_id":"dastyMwwpup3GhTh","name":"Prédateur de l'hiver [Cercle des Saisons]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-monster-grin-purple-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"predateur-de-l-hiver\"><strong>Pr&eacute;dateur de l'hiver</strong></h3>\n<p>L'hiver, la lutte pour la survie est &acirc;pre et vous devez vous adapter pour r&eacute;sister aux puissants pr&eacute;dateurs qui parcourent les &eacute;tendues gel&eacute;es. &Agrave; partir du niveau 14, vous pouvez vous transformer en un terrible pr&eacute;dateur lorsque vous utilisez votre aptitude de @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.qribBuHAI1PBTu9I]{Forme sauvage [Druide]}. Vous pouvez prendre la forme d'une b&ecirc;te dont l'indice de dangerosit&eacute; peut aller jusqu'&agrave; 2. De plus, lorsque vous &ecirc;tes sous forme sauvage, vous obtenez la r&eacute;sistance au feu et au froid. Malgr&eacute; son nom, vous b&eacute;n&eacute;ficiez de cette aptitude quelle que soit la saison.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685477,"modifiedTime":1663923687153,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Attaque de second rang [Philaxien]","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/glaive-simple.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1hSTXfYoiyFkzr3G"}},"_id":"dcRsvdPcSkpKdD9t","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 10, lorsque vous utilisez une lance ou une arme dotée de la propriété allonge, vous pouvez attaquer depuis une position située derrière un allié de taille moyenne ou inférieure.</p>\n<p>Vous ne devez pas être à plus de 1,50 m de la cible et devez attaquer la même cible que l'allié derrière lequel vous êtes placé.</p>\n<p>Cette attaque est réalisée avec un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">désavantage</a>. Vous êtes considéré comme bénéficiant d'un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#abri\">abri partiel</a> contre la créature que vous attaquez. Si vous portez un bouclier, vous êtes considéré comme bénéficiant d'un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#abri\">abri important</a></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685478,"modifiedTime":1663923687155,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"dca1yAK6QZ1ypaHD","name":"Résistance supérieure [Lignée infernale]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-diamond-red.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"resistance-superieure\"><strong>R&eacute;sistance sup&eacute;rieure</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; mesure que la magie de votre lign&eacute;e coule dans vos veines, elle fait &eacute;merger la r&eacute;sistance des fi&eacute;lons aux agressions &eacute;l&eacute;mentaires.</p>\n<p>Au niveau 14, en d&eacute;pensant 1 point de sorcellerie et une action bonus, vous obtenez la r&eacute;sistance aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de feu, de foudre et de froid pendant un nombre de minutes &eacute;gal &agrave; votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Ensorceleur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685478,"modifiedTime":1663923687158,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"dlC4QSoQtxqnwdmS","name":"Magie extra-dimensionnelle [Entité extra-dimensionnelle]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/creatures/unholy/demon-winged-cyclops-drooling.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"magie-extra-dimensionnelle\"><strong>Magie extra-dimensionnelle</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 10, la nature de votre magie est si &eacute;trange et incompr&eacute;hensible que les victimes de vos sorts sont d&eacute;sorient&eacute;es. &Agrave; chaque fois que vous infligez des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts &agrave; une cr&eacute;ature au moyen d'un sort, elle subit un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">d&eacute;savantage</a>&nbsp;&agrave; tous ses tests &agrave; son prochain tour &agrave; moins de r&eacute;ussir un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a> de Sagesse dont la difficult&eacute; est &eacute;gale &agrave; la moiti&eacute; des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts subis (avec un DD maximum de 20 &agrave; partir de 40 points de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685479,"modifiedTime":1663923687160,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"dmaWjVM57R2IxaoT","name":"Élémentaliste - Feu [Élémentaliste]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/hand-sparks-glow-yellow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"elementaliste\"><strong>&Eacute;l&eacute;mentaliste</strong></h3>\n<p>Lorsque vous choisissez cette voie au niveau 2, vous d&eacute;terminez quel est votre &eacute;l&eacute;ment de pr&eacute;dilection : l'air, l'eau, le feu ou la terre. Ce choix va fa&ccedil;onner votre identit&eacute; et influencer les autres &eacute;tapes de votre carri&egrave;re.</p>\n<p><strong>Feu</strong>. Vous &ecirc;tes le ma&icirc;tre de l'&eacute;l&eacute;ment le plus spectaculaire et le plus destructeur de tous. Vous voyez autour de vous un monde destin&eacute; &agrave; br&ucirc;ler, et vous pouvez manipuler ce feu pour qu'il consume vos ennemis. Vous avez &eacute;galement appris que le feu peut purifier et prot&eacute;ger s'il est bien contr&ocirc;l&eacute;. Les &eacute;l&eacute;mentalistes du feu m&eacute;prisent g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement les pouvoirs de l'eau qui, le plus souvent, apaisent et refroidissent.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spe