{"_id":"ge5HuHFYXg7tqoqV","name":"Vigilance primitive [Rôdeur]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/perception/hand-eye-pink.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"vigilance-primitive\"><strong>Vigilance primitive</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 3, vous pouvez utiliser une action et d&eacute;penser un emplacement de sort de r&ocirc;deur pour exacerber votre vigilance et ouvrir vos sens &agrave; la r&eacute;gion qui vous entoure. Pendant un nombre de minutes &eacute;quivalent au niveau de l'emplacement de sort que vous avez d&eacute;pens&eacute;, vous pouvez d&eacute;terminer si les cr&eacute;atures des types suivants se trouvent dans un rayon de 1,5 kilom&egrave;tre de vous (si vous &ecirc;tes sur votre terrain de pr&eacute;dilection, ce rayon est de 9 kilom&egrave;tres) : aberrations, c&eacute;lestes, dragons, &eacute;l&eacute;mentaires, f&eacute;es, fi&eacute;lons et morts-vivants. Cette aptitude ne vous permet pas de savoir o&ugrave; se trouvent ces cr&eacute;atures, ni leur nombre.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charge