{"_id":"hpptQ7BxIrf7dxIW","name":"Châtiment divin [Paladin]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-yellow-teal.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"chatiment-divin\"><strong>Ch&acirc;timent divin</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 2, quand vous touchez une cr&eacute;ature avec une arme de corps-&agrave;-corps, vous pouvez utiliser un emplacement de sort pour infliger des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts radiants &agrave; cette cr&eacute;ature en plus des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts normaux de l'arme. Vous infligez 2d8 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts suppl&eacute;mentaires si vous utilisez un emplacement de sort de niveau 1, auquel vous ajoutez 1d8 par niveau de sort suppl&eacute;mentaire, jusqu'&agrave; un maximum de 5d8. Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts subis sont augment&eacute;s d'1d8 suppl&eacute;mentaire si la cible est un mort-vivant ou un fi&eacute;lon.</p>\n<h3 id=\"chatiment-divin-ameliore\"><strong>Ch&acirc;timent divin am&eacute;lior&eacute;</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 11, vous d&eacute;bordez tellement de vertu que tous les coups que vous portez avec vos armes de corps-&agrave;-corps sont aliment&eacute;s par de l'&eacute;nergie divine. Quand vous touchez une cr&eacute;ature avec une arme de corps-&agrave;-corps, celle-ci subit 1d8 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts radiants suppl&eacute;mentaires. Si vous utilisez aussi votre ch&acirc;timent divin lors d'une attaque, vous additionnez ces d&eacute;g&acirc;ts aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts suppl&eacute;mentaires de votre ch&acirc;timent divin.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685584,"modifiedTime":1663923687331,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"hsvicJDLuDnEUasx","name":"Résistance surhumaine [Défenseur]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/shield/buckler-wooden-boss-glowing-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"resistance-surhumaine\"><strong>R&eacute;sistance surhumaine</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 18, lorsque vous n'avez pas plus de la moiti&eacute; de vos points de vie, vous gagnez les b&eacute;n&eacute;fices suivants :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>La r&eacute;sistance aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts tranchants, per&ccedil;ants et contondants si vous portez une armure lourde.</li>\n<li>La r&eacute;sistance aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts tranchants, per&ccedil;ants et contondants non magiques si vous portez une armure interm&eacute;diaire.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685585,"modifiedTime":1663923687334,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
