{"name":"Par le sang, la puissance [Mortifié]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-area-circle-red-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TISBWzjToXlPed5Y"}},"_id":"ijpj2LytrghQL0UV","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 2, lorsque vous utilisez votre action pour lancer un sort, il est possible d'utiliser votre action bonus pour vous scarifier et ainsi l'améliorer.</p>\n<p>Au choix, vous pouvez soit dépenser une canalisation d'énergie divine ou sacrifier 1d6 PV : cela vous permet de lancer le sort avec un emplacement de sort d'un niveau au-dessus de son niveau normal.</p>\n<p>Vous ne pouvez jamais utiliser cette aptitude pour augmenter le niveau d'un sort qui produit des soins. Vous ne pouvez pas augmenter de plus d'un niveau l'emplacement du sort de cette façon.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685592,"modifiedTime":1663923687356,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"inxIgdIB8y0KD4P7","name":"Incantations [Sorcelame]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/water/water-hand.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h4 id=\"incantations\"><strong>Incantations</strong></h4>\n<p>Tout comme l'ensorceleur, votre magie coule dans vos veines et elle est bas&eacute;e sur la force de votre ego.</p>\n<p>Difficult&eacute; des jets de sauvegarde = 8 + bonus de ma&icirc;trise + modificateur de Charisme</p>\n<p>Modificateur d'attaque des sorts = bonus de ma&icirc;trise + modificateur de Charisme</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez utiliser une arme de corps-&agrave;-corps comme focaliseur d'incantation pour vos sorts d'ensorceleur.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685593,"modifiedTime":1663923687359,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
