{"_id":"kOCDaMSafDcQvCRs","name":"Guérisseur émérite [Cercle de la Vie]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-worn-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lM8e7Ci4oAsat70d"},"rest-recovery":{"data":{"recovery":{"enabled":false}}},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Gu&eacute;risseur &eacute;m&eacute;rite</strong></h3>\n<p>Toujours au niveau 2, vous obtenez la ma&icirc;trise de la comp&eacute;tence M&eacute;decine. Si vous l&rsquo;avez d&eacute;j&agrave;, vous doublez votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise quand vous l&rsquo;utilisez.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez d&eacute;penser une de vos m&eacute;tamorphoses afin de lancer le sort @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.k2lRJF0cIp0fJn5I]{Soin des blessures}. Il est consid&eacute;r&eacute; comme &eacute;tant lanc&eacute; avec un emplacement d&rsquo;un niveau &eacute;gal &agrave; la moiti&eacute; de votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise, arrondi &agrave; l&rsquo;inf&eacute;rieur.</p>\n<p>Enfin, quand vous lancez un sort de soins, vous ajoutez votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise au nombre de points de vie que vous rendez.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #3","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"