{"name":"Maître des ombres [Ombrelin]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/perception/silhouette-stealth-shadow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xU19Zisgb17aX92J"}},"_id":"l4Fz6JaRPIfBMkJR","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 15, votre maîtrise des ténèbres s'étend aux zones de lumière faible (pénombre) et même à toutes celles où la visibilité est réduite (brume légère, végétation luxuriante).</p>\n<p>Désormais vous pouvez y utiliser vos aptitudes @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.9VcMPDISJfTuXdJ1]{Un coup dans le noir [Ombrelin]} et @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.xzCKGfjeSmJEZpsO]{Ruse [Ombrelin]}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rodeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685608,"modifiedTime":1663923687418,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"lRWhSvQ7H42g5e6Q","name":"Froid comme la mort [Voie des glace]","type":"feat","img":"icons/creatures/abilities/fangs-teeth-bite.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.qRmD6eUoB1vKMTzu"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Au niveau 10, votre corps devient si résilient qu'il est capable d'endurer le froid glacial de la mort. Votre résistance au froid (voir @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.957MxwWr1DT64y6e]{Rage froide [Voie des glaces]}) s'étend aux dégâts nécrotiques.</p>\n<p>De plus, les morts-vivants ont des difficultés à vous distinguer des morts et subissent un <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">désavantage</a> pour vous attaquer.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Barbare","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685608,"modifiedTime":1663923687420,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
