{"_id":"lXUqdzWRNrmielmG","name":"Maîtrise - Enchantement [Académicien]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kaN0yX2o4iTjrs4N"}},"img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Enchantement</span></strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong>Pr&eacute;sence envo&ucirc;tante :</strong>&nbsp;Si vous n'avez pas attaqu&eacute; une cr&eacute;ature, lorsque celle-ci vous attaque, elle doit auparavant r&eacute;ussir un&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"> de Sagesse ou perdre son action &agrave; ce tour. Le DD est &eacute;gal &agrave; celui de vos sorts de magicien. Au round suivant, elle peut vous attaquer normalement. Cette aptitude n'affecte pas les cr&eacute;atures qui ne peuvent &ecirc;tre&nbsp;charm&eacute;es.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"JdS Echec : La cible perd son tour","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","