{"_id":"nzY82Aoocnc4U3lm","name":"Parangon héroïque [Serment de Perfection]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-strong-blue-yellow.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"parangon-heroique\"><strong>Parangon h&eacute;ro&iuml;que</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 20, au prix d'une action, vous pouvez devenir un parangon d'h&eacute;ro&iuml;sme. Pendant 1 minute, votre peau prend la teinte de l'or pur et &eacute;met une faible lumi&egrave;re dor&eacute;e dans un rayon de 6 m&egrave;tres autour de vous. De plus, vous devenez r&eacute;sistant &agrave; tous les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts subis et vous obtenez un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a> &agrave; toutes vos attaques au corps-&agrave;-corps, ainsi que vos tests de Force, de Constitution, de Sagesse et de Charisme (jets de sauvegarde et tests de comp&eacute;tence). Vous devez terminer un repos long avant de pouvoir de nouveau utiliser cette aptitude.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685624,"modifiedTime":1663923687477,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
