{"_id":"pOQwxihVqXK09dBA","name":"Canalisation divine : Vie - Salve de guérison [Prêtre]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.40IqyVEFjZYO474e"}},"img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-orange-small.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine : Vie [Pr&ecirc;tre] Salve de gu&eacute;rison</strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Vous et jusqu'&agrave; cinq alli&eacute;s dans votre champ de vision, dans un rayon de 9 m&egrave;tres autour de vous, r&eacute;cup&eacute;rez 1d6 points de vie par point de bonus de ma&icirc;trise.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":9,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"Jusqu'à 5 cibles + le lanceur","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["(@prof)d6","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685635,"modifiedTime":1663923687525,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"pPbesWgASIEowHJx","name":"Second souffle [Guerrier]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-glowing-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"second-souffle\"><strong>Second souffle</strong></h3>\n<p>Vous jouissez d'une r&eacute;serve limit&eacute;e d'endurance dans laquelle vous pouvez puiser afin de vous prot&eacute;ger. Lors de votre tour, vous pouvez utiliser une action bonus pour regagner un nombre de points de vie &eacute;gal &agrave; 1d10 + votre niveau de guerrier. Une fois que vous avez utilis&eacute; cette aptitude, vous devez finir un repos court ou un repos long avant de l'utiliser de nouveau.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10 + @classes.guerrier.levels","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOv