{"_id":"sBxgQeGbLHt7Nm8u","name":"Maître des traditions [Gardien des Traditions]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/sundries/documents/document-sealed-red-yellow.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"maitre-des-traditions\"><strong>Ma&icirc;tre des traditions</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 17, vous obtenez deux points de caract&eacute;ristiques suppl&eacute;mentaires que vous pouvez ajouter au choix en Sagesse ou en Charisme. Vous pouvez choisir de r&eacute;partir un point en Sagesse et l'autre en Charisme. Votre maximum pour ces deux valeurs est &agrave; pr&eacute;sent de 22.</p>\n<p>D&eacute;sormais, vous &ecirc;tes capable de lancer le sort@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.AbpUeHdRgmQyzsK1]{Soin des blessures de groupe} en utilisant une action bonus et @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.EE8nPIyioWTbfpUG]{Mot de gu&eacute;rison de groupe}&nbsp;en utilisant une r&eacute;action (donc en dehors de votre propre tour).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685654,"modifiedTime":1663923687601,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
