{"_id":"sWROtvhxWJLzvxsC","name":"Soutien puissant [Guide Spirituel]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-spiral-white.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"soutien-puissant\"><strong>Soutien puissant</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 8, si vous utilisez une action pour lancer @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.ET8WtXuEifdjbtp8]{Assistance}&nbsp;ou @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.djoMzjTA610GQAv4]{R&eacute;sistance}, votre cible obtient un bonus d'1d6 au lieu d'1d4. Le bonus passe &agrave; 1d8 au niveau 14 et 1d10 au niveau 17. D&eacute;sormais, lorsque vous maintenez votre concentration sur l'un de ces sorts, vous ne pouvez plus &ecirc;tre involontairement d&eacute;concentr&eacute;.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685657,"modifiedTime":1663923687620,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"sXZmTfBy4PHas9xf","name":"Fureur du dragon [Voie des Cinq Animaux]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/creatures/abilities/dragon-ice-breath-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"fureur-du-dragon\"><strong>Fureur du dragon</strong></h3>\n<p>Lorsque vous atteignez le niveau 17, en d&eacute;pensant 3 points de ki, vous pouvez utiliser votre action pour porter une attaque &agrave; mains nues contre chaque cr&eacute;ature autour de vous dans un rayon de 4,50 m&egrave;tres. La r&eacute;ussite de votre attaque est automatique et vous infligez vos d&eacute;g&acirc;t &agrave; mains nues normaux. Chaque cr&eacute;ature de taille moyenne ou inf&eacute;rieure que vous blessez par cette attaque doit r&eacute;ussir un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Force (DD = 8 + votre modificateur de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute; + votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise) ou se retrouver&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#a-terre\">&agrave; terre</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":4.5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":3},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"JdS Echec : Cible à terre","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"dex"},"requirements":"Moine","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685657,"modifiedTime":1663923687622,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
