{"name":"Par la punition, le renouveau [Mortifié]","type":"feat","img":"icons/commodities/metal/clasp-steel-green.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ieHHiRO2UpYwmcZH"}},"_id":"tOzQQR7yxJ96MinG","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 8, pendant un repos court, vous vous infligez de multiples et légères scarifications tout en entrant dans un état méditatif profond.</p>\n<p>Certains mortifiés ne se scarifient pas mais s'infligent brûlures et autres punitions corporelles visibles.</p>\n<p>Vous récupérez un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou 3 que vous avez dépensé. Vous n'obtenez aucun autre bénéfice durant ce repos court. Vous pouvez utiliser cette aptitude une fois entre deux repos longs</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685665,"modifiedTime":1663923687659,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"tQqmviwHfR0alhEb","name":"Enfant de l'ombre [Ombrelame]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/sundries/lights/lantern-iron-yellow.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"enfant-de-l-ombre\"><strong>Enfant de l'ombre</strong></h3>\n<p>&Eacute;galement au niveau 3, en utilisant une action bonus, vous pouvez d&eacute;signer une source de lumi&egrave;re non magique &agrave; une port&eacute;e de 18 m&egrave;tres et r&eacute;duire de moiti&eacute; le rayon de lumi&egrave;re vive qu'elle &eacute;met pendant 1 minute. La zone de lumi&egrave;re faible n'est pas affect&eacute;e. Par exemple, une torche voit sa zone de lumi&egrave;re vive r&eacute;duite &agrave; 3 m&egrave;tres, mais sa zone de lumi&egrave;re faible reste de 6 m&egrave;tres. Si la source de lumi&egrave;re est magique, vous devez d&eacute;penser 1 point de sorcellerie par niveau du sort (aucun point pour un tour de magie).</p>\n<p>De plus, vous obtenez un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a> aux tests de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute; (Discr&eacute;tion) que vous effectuez dans une zone de lumi&egrave;re faible.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":18,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Roublard","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685666,"modifiedTime":166