{"_id":"uQx4uWh3M99xtWuQ","name":"Prière de soins [Lignée céleste]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/light/orbs-hand-gray.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"priere-de-soins\"><strong>Pri&egrave;re de soins</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 14, en d&eacute;pensant 3 points de sorcellerie, vous pouvez lancer le sort @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.zOHt9ucevU9YJgXx]{Pri&egrave;re de soins} au niveau 2. Vous pouvez d&eacute;penser davantage de points de sorcellerie pour le lancer avec un emplacement de sort sup&eacute;rieur : vous utilisez pour cela le tableau de cr&eacute;ation d'emplacements de sort de l'ensorceleur (voir @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.qi2ybvnH4vG4CIYN]{Source de Magie [Ensorceleur]}). Vous devez terminer un repos court ou long avant de pouvoir utiliser de nouveau cette aptitude.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":10,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":3},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Ensorceleur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685675,"modifiedTime":1663923687699,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"uVGIOy2NVSDBbcfu","name":"Puissance vengeresse [Cercle des Châtiments]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Puissance vengeresse</strong></h3>\n<p>Lorsque vous lancez un tour de magie infligeant des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts, vous pouvez ajouter votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s par le sort.</p>\n<p>De plus, vous obtenez le tour de magie @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.OIUJrZVZ8nqLLqiv]{Gourdin magique} s&rsquo;il ne fait pas partie de votre liste de sorts. Vous pouvez aussi ajouter votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s par un gourdin ou un b&acirc;ton enchant&eacute; par ce tour de magie.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #4","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685675,"modifiedTime":1663923687701,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"uVzqCWVhWrlg3PVc","name":"Initiation [Voie des esprits]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/nature/beam-hand-leaves-green.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"initiation\"><strong>Initiation&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n<p>&Eacute;galement au niveau 3, &agrave; la suite d'une c&eacute;r&eacute;monie, vous entrez en communion avec un esprit animal : ours, taureau (ou bison), loup, chouette, aigle, renard, lynx (ou tout autre f&eacute;lin), etc. L'animal qui correspond &agrave; votre alter ego spirituel ne vous est jamais hostile et vous b&eacute;n&eacute;ficiez d'un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;aux tests lorsque vous essayez de le pister, de le rep&eacute;rer, de l'influencer ou de le dresser.</p>\n<p>En d&eacute;pensant un point de lien spirituel, vous pouvez utiliser sur vous-m&ecirc;me le sort @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.6KPbqosOjwrNiKMf]{Am&eacute;lioration de caract&eacute;ristique}, mais uniquement dans la version qui correspond &agrave; l'esprit auquel vous &ecirc;tes li&eacute;. Le loup permet d'am&eacute;liorer la Sagesse (comme la chouette) et le lynx correspond au chat et permet d'am&eacute;liorer la Dext&eacute;rit&eacute;. Vous pouvez bien entendu choisir d'autres animaux et la caract&eacute;ristique correspondante en accord avec votre MJ. Si vous choisissez un animal associ&eacute; &agrave; l'Intelligence, la Sagesse ou le Charisme (loup, chouette, aigle, renard), votre valeur de lien spirituel est augment&eacute;e de un.</p>\n<p>Vous &ecirc;tes capable de maintenir une concentration lorsque vous &ecirc;tes sous les effets de la rage ; toutefois, cela ne concerne que les sorts obtenus par la voie des esprits.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Barbare","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685676,"modifiedTime":1663923687704,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"uX61q1op1Q1k8XPn","name":"Garde du corps [Défenseur]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/defensive/illusion-evasion-echo-purple.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"garde-du-corps\"><strong>Garde du corps</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 7, lorsqu'une cr&eacute;ature attaque un alli&eacute; situ&eacute; &agrave; moins de 1,50 m&egrave;tre de vous, vous pouvez utiliser votre r&eacute;action pour devenir la cible de l'attaque &agrave; sa place. Cette aptitude fonctionne pour tout type d'attaque qui n&eacute;cessite un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#jets-d-attaque\">jet d'attaque</a> (au corps-&agrave;-corps, &agrave; distance ou par sort). Vous devez annoncer votre intention avant que le r&eacute;sultat de l'attaque soit connu. Si l'attaque vous inflige des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts, vous obtenez la r&eacute;sistance &agrave; ces d&eacute;g&acirc;ts.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"allié à moins de 1m50"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685677,"modifiedTime":1663923687707,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
