{"_id":"veRQVbYCeHUxCe0Q","name":"Frappe étourdissante [Moine]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"midiProperties":{"nodam":false,"fulldam":false,"halfdam":false,"rollOther":false,"critOther":false,"magicdam":false,"magiceffect":false,"concentration":false,"toggleEffect":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"frappe-etourdissante\"><strong>Frappe &eacute;tourdissante</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 5, vous pouvez interf&eacute;rer avec le flux du ki d'un de vos adversaires. Quand vous frappez une autre cr&eacute;ature avec une arme de moine ou &agrave; mains nues, vous pouvez d&eacute;penser 1 point de ki pour tenter de r&eacute;aliser une frappe &eacute;tourdissante. La cible doit r&eacute;ussir un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#jets-de-sauvegarde\">jet de sauvegarde</a>&nbsp;de Constitution ou elle sera&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#etourdi\">&eacute;tourdie</a> jusqu'&agrave; la fin de votre prochain tour.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc"