{"_id":"wWa9W4VLy7uBVac5","name":"Aura de Courage [Paladin]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-yellow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"aura-de-courage\"><strong>Aura de courage</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 10, vous, ainsi que toute cr&eacute;ature amicale qui se trouve &agrave; 3 m&egrave;tres de vous, ne pouvez &ecirc;tre&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#terrorise\">terroris&eacute;s</a>. Cette aura persiste tant que vous n'&ecirc;tes pas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/gerer-la-sante-du-personnage/#inconscient\">inconscient</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"perm"},"target":{"value":3,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"di.value.terrorisé","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685688,"modifiedTime":1663923687760,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"wXCuQEgYRDL68kri","name":"Canalisation divine : Terre - Enfouissement [Prêtre]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.40IqyVEFjZYO474e"}},"img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-orange-small.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine : Terre - Enfouissement</strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Vous pouvez vous d&eacute;placer &agrave; travers la pierre ou la terre d'un sol ou d'une paroi, s'ils sont naturels, &agrave; la moiti&eacute; de votre vitesse normale pendant un nombre de rounds &eacute;gal &agrave; votre bonus de ma&icirc;trise. Lorsque l'aptitude se termine, si vous restez prisonnier dans la mati&egrave;re, vous &ecirc;tes &eacute;ject&eacute; vers l'espace libre le plus proche, vous subissez 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts contondants par m&egrave;tre de mati&egrave;re travers&eacute;e, et vous &ecirc;tes &eacute;tourdi pendant 1 round.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685689,"modifiedTime":1663923687764,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"wehEBNGo06eXy42B","name":"Guérisseur de pacotille [Cercle des Châtiments]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/life/heart-glowing-red.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong>Gu&eacute;risseur de pacotille</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 2, vous d&eacute;cidez de vous concentrer davantage sur les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s par vos sorts que sur le soutien &agrave; vos alli&eacute;s.</p>\n<p>Lorsque vous lancez les d&eacute;s afin de d&eacute;terminer le nombre de points de vie rendus par un sort de gu&eacute;rison rendant des PV (comme @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.k2lRJF0cIp0fJn5I]{Soin des blessures}, @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.q4YQyD1xulTcHEgm]{Mot de gu&eacute;rison} ou @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.AbpUeHdRgmQyzsK1]{Soin des blessures de groupe} par exemple), vous ne pouvez pas ajouter votre bonus de caract&eacute;ristique au nombre de points de vie rendus si le sort le permet.</p>\n<p>Vous devez en outre relancer les d&eacute;s ayant obtenu le maximum (8 sur 1d8 par exemple) puis utiliser le nouveau r&eacute;sultat.</p>\n<p>De plus, tout sort rendant un nombre fixe de points de vie ne rend que la moiti&eacute; du nombre pr&eacute;vu.</p>\n<p>Enfin, cette r&egrave;gle s&rsquo;applique m&ecirc;me aux sorts obtenus via des dons, des objets magiques ou un multiclassage</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Gazette R'n P #4","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Druide","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685690,"modifiedTime":1663923687766,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
