{"_id":"xLtStJ2iS5Kr9O35","name":"Style de combat supplémentaire  [Défenseur]","type":"feat","flags":{"entityorder":{"order":118}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-purple.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"style-de-combat-supplementaire-2\"><strong>Style de combat suppl&eacute;mentaire</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n<p>Au niveau 10, vous pouvez choisir un deuxi&egrave;me style de combat parmi d&eacute;fense ou protection.</p>\n<p>De plus, vos r&eacute;flexes incroyables vous permettent d'utiliser une de vos aptitudes parmi @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.CKu148hXnq8Rzuv2]{Bloquer un adversaire [D&eacute;fenseur]} et @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-capacites-de-classes.uX61q1op1Q1k8XPn]{Garde du corps [D&eacute;fenseur]} au moment de votre choix dans le round, sans utiliser de r&eacute;action. Vous pouvez normalement utiliser votre r&eacute;action pour tout autre usage l&eacute;gal au m&ecirc;me round, cela vous permet &eacute;ventuellement une seconde utilisation d'une de ces aptitudes.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Guerrier","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"featType":{"value":"passive","_deprecated":true,"type":"String","label":"Feat Type"},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e",