{"_id":"xrlq1CtMp01MasOT","name":"Canalisation d'énergie divine : Magie puissante [Clerc Théurge]","type":"feat","flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-yellow-blue-large.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"canalisation-d-energie-divine-magie-puissante\"><strong>Canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine : Magie puissante</strong></h3>\n<p>Lorsque vous atteignez le niveau 8, vous am&eacute;liorez l'efficacit&eacute; de magie renforc&eacute;e. D&eacute;sormais, vous pouvez utiliser votre canalisation d'&eacute;nergie divine pour lancer un sort de deux niveaux au-dessus de l'emplacement de sort utilis&eacute; (mais jamais au-dessus du niveau 9).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Clerc","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685697,"modifiedTime":1663923687794,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"name":"Ruse [Ombrelin]","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/perception/mask-stone-eyes-orange.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tYXHEOTl1Rlu4hDz"}},"_id":"xzCKGfjeSmJEZpsO","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>À partir du niveau 11, votre aisance dans l'obscurité vous permet de vous déplacer et d'agir rapidement.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez bénéficier d'une action bonus à chacun de vos tours de combat.</p>\n<p>Par contre, cette action ne peut être utilisée que pour accomplir les actions <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#se-precipiter\">se précipiter</a>,<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#se-desengager\"> se désengager</a> ou <a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#se-cacher\">se cacher</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Pangée","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rodeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"yGhpLZcgKkBfBfgm":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685698,"modifiedTime":1663923687796,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"y4ABxQonpespGSJU","name":"Maîtrise - Illusion [Académicien]","type":"feat","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.P4aJQKXB4qmgCLsN"}},"img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Illusion</span></strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong>Sort illusoire</strong> : Vous pouvez lancer un sort de l'&eacute;cole d'&eacute;vocation ou d'invocation que vous connaissez sous forme d'illusion (mais il garde son &eacute;cole d'origine). Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s sont de type psychique, mais les cibles pensent qu'il s'agit du type de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts appropri&eacute; au sort imit&eacute;. Un alli&eacute; ou une cr&eacute;ature pr&eacute;venue de la nature de l'illusion obtient une r&eacute;sistance aux d&eacute;g&acirc;ts du sort.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuels de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Magicien","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"qfQAJ4nuEz9djwAx":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685698,"modifiedTime":1663923687799,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"y5Ey9omrVU3Q0src","name":"Attaque supplémentaire [Barbare]","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/spear-tips-triple-orange.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"_sheetTab":"description","entityorder":{"order":200},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false},"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"attaque-supplementaire\"><strong>Attaque suppl&eacute;mentaire</strong></h3>\n<p>&Agrave; partir du niveau 5, vous pouvez attaquer deux fois au lieu d'une quand vous choisissez l'action&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#attaquer\">attaquer</a> lors de votre tour.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Barbare niveau 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685699,"modifiedTime":1663923687801,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"y8EZwclPIgiHCilx","name":"Héritage Féerique [Lignée féerique]","type":"feat","flags":{},"img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-green.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"heritage-feerique\"><strong>H&eacute;ritage f&eacute;erique</strong></h3>\n<p>Vous avez h&eacute;rit&eacute; de la beaut&eacute; &eacute;th&eacute;r&eacute;e des f&eacute;es. D&egrave;s le niveau 1, vous b&eacute;n&eacute;ficiez d'un&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\">avantage</a>&nbsp;&agrave; tous les tests de Charisme destin&eacute;s &agrave; s&eacute;duire ou charmer.</p>\n<p>De plus, vous avez une affinit&eacute; pour les armes de la for&ecirc;t, au premier niveau vous acqu&eacute;rez la ma&icirc;trise de l'arc court et de la lance.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Ensorceleur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685699,"modifiedTime":1663923687803,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
{"_id":"yBp0Htz1pey4dhBq","name":"Style de combat : Arme à deux mains [Guerrier - Paladin]","type":"feat","flags":{"entityorder":{"order":197}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-steel-yellow.webp","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"armes-a-deux-mains\"><strong>Armes &agrave; deux mains</strong></h3>\n<p>Quand vous faites 1 ou 2 avec un d&eacute; de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts pour une attaque avec une arme de corps-&agrave;-corps tenue &agrave; deux mains, vous pouvez lancer de nouveau le d&eacute; et vous devez utiliser ce second r&eacute;sultat, m&ecirc;me s'il s'agit encore d'un 1 ou d'un 2. L'arme doit avoir la propri&eacute;t&eacute; &agrave; deux mains ou poss&eacute;der la propri&eacute;t&eacute; polyvalente pour que vous puissiez b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier de cette aptitude.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Guerrier / Paladin","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685700,"modifiedTime":1663923687805,"lastModifiedBy":"jxF0Pjz3E2EU23q5"}}
