{"_id":"zGdMkRc0yBr8jkMh","name":"Tueur d'ennemis [Rôdeur]","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/bows/shortbow-recurve-yellow.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"flags":{"magicitems":{"enabled":false,"equipped":false,"attuned":false,"charges":"0","chargeType":"c1","destroy":false,"destroyFlavorText":"a atteint 0 charges : les mots sur le parchemin disparaissent, et il tombe en poussière.","rechargeable":false,"recharge":"0","rechargeType":"t1","rechargeUnit":"r1","sorting":"l"}},"system":{"description":{"value":"<h3 id=\"tueur-d-ennemis\"><strong>Tueur d'ennemis</strong></h3>\n<p>Au niveau 20, vous avez d&eacute;velopp&eacute; un talent exceptionnel pour &eacute;liminer vos ennemis. Une fois par tour, vous pouvez utiliser cette aptitude pour ajouter votre modificateur de Sagesse au&nbsp;<a href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/combattre/#jets-d-attaque\">jet d'attaque</a>&nbsp;ou de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts d'une attaque port&eacute;e contre un de vos ennemis jur&eacute;s. Vous pouvez choisir d'utiliser cette aptitude avant ou apr&egrave;s avoir jet&eacute; les d&eacute;s, mais vous devez vous &ecirc;tre d&eacute;cid&eacute; avant que les effets de ce jet aient &eacute;t&eacute; appliqu&eacute;s.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel de Règles","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Rôdeur","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0,"YXEVHqx5k2ArOvJE":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1663923685707,"modifiedTime":1663923